<i>noun</i>: 무도 [무ː도], 기사도 [기사도] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>무도 [무ː도]</dt><br>
<dd>1. martial arts</dd><br>
<dd>무술이나 무예.</dd><br>
<dd>Martial arts or a talent for martial arts.</dd><br>
<dd>2. knighthood; chivalry</dd><br>
<dd>무사가 지녀야 할 예의와 도리.</dd><br>
<dd>A code of conduct and virtues that a warrior is expected to follow.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>기사도 [기사도]</dt><br>
<dd>1. chivalry</dd><br>
<dd>중세 유럽에서 기사들이 지켜야 했던 규범이나 행동 양식.</dd><br>
<dd>Norms or patterns of behavior to be respected by knights during medieval times in Europe.</dd><br>
<dd>2. chivalry</dd><br>
<dd>여자를 보호하고 의리와 정의를 지키며 예절이 바른 남자의 규범.</dd><br>
<dd>Norms applied to men to protect women, abide by principles of loyalty and justice, and be courteous.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>